1
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:04,760
The Imperial Clan Court's Archive Pavilion.

2
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,300
The last files my father reviewed

3
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:07,230
are right there.

4
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:07,900
Mr. Shen.

5
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,100
My mother was a distant branch of the royal family.

6
00:01:10,100 --> 00:01:11,800
I visited the Imperial Clan Court with her when I was young.

7
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:13,460
I remember the Archive Pavilion is in the northeast courtyard.

8
00:01:13,460 --> 00:01:14,660
It's a three-story wooden building.

9
00:01:14,660 --> 00:01:16,460
There is an old guard named Zhao San at the west corner gate.

10
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:19,320
He slacks off and dozes off every night at midnight.

11
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,160
Miss Gu.

12
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:22,960
Can you remember anything else?

13
00:01:23,330 --> 00:01:23,960
Like,

14
00:01:24,500 --> 00:01:25,630
the interior layout.

15
00:01:25,630 --> 00:01:26,400
Inside the pavilion,

16
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:28,930
there's a portrait of Xiao Chong'an in the northwest corner.

17
00:01:28,930 --> 00:01:29,990
My father once said

18
00:01:30,230 --> 00:01:32,300
that Lord Xiao was proficient in feng shui and mechanisms.

19
00:01:32,300 --> 00:01:33,430
If he hid something,

20
00:01:33,700 --> 00:01:35,460
it must be out of sight.

21
00:01:36,100 --> 00:01:37,200
Out of sight.

22
00:01:37,930 --> 00:01:39,190
The northwest corner,

23
00:01:39,500 --> 00:01:40,300
the portrait.

24
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,030
Help me hold him.

25
00:01:57,330 --> 00:01:59,560
We must find a way to break the contract as soon as possible.

26
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,560
The Imperial Clan Court.

27
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,430
We'll go tonight.

28
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:02,460
You guys stay here

29
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:03,990
and wait for my news.

30
00:02:35,130 --> 00:02:35,760
Tung oil.

31
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:37,430
The oil stains are fresh.

32
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,560
Someone has been here recently.

33
00:02:52,900 --> 00:02:53,430
Someone.

34
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:56,060
They are also looking for something.

35
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:27,700
Mechanism wires.

36
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,360
They trigger upon touch.

37
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:47,960
Brother Xiao,

38
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:50,020
you still like playing these tricks.

39
00:04:04,230 --> 00:04:04,960
Nephew Shen,

40
00:04:05,230 --> 00:04:06,290
since you're here,

41
00:04:06,660 --> 00:04:08,390
why not show yourself and talk?

42
00:04:09,330 --> 00:04:10,530
Good tactics, Lord Qin.

43
00:04:10,530 --> 00:04:11,730
You're even familiar

44
00:04:11,730 --> 00:04:12,900
with the mechanisms set by Lord Xiao.

45
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:15,200
Brother Xiao and I were once from the same sect.

46
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:15,700
Nephew,

47
00:04:16,260 --> 00:04:17,700
you've been investigating all along,

48
00:04:17,700 --> 00:04:19,200
isn't it just for the truth?

49
00:04:19,200 --> 00:04:20,630
Your father, Shen Qingshan,

50
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:22,560
didn't disappear seven years ago.

51
00:04:22,730 --> 00:04:24,860
Instead, he took the initiative to infiltrate them,

52
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:25,630
using himself as bait

53
00:04:25,630 --> 00:04:26,690
to set up this trap.

54
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:29,030
The three copper coins are three keys.

55
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,030
Only by collecting them all can you open

56
00:04:31,030 --> 00:04:32,690
the map to the Tianji Pavilion

57
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:34,430
and find the ultimate answer.

58
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:35,800
About your father's whereabouts,

59
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:37,760
about the whole truth of the Dragon Vein Soul Eater.

60
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:38,830
Why should I believe you?

61
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:39,700
Just based on this

62
00:04:39,700 --> 00:04:40,930
secret letter your father entrusted me to keep

63
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:42,000
the night before he disappeared.

64
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:42,460
He said,

65
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,200
'If Mo insists on tracking this down,

66
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,000
then tell him about this letter

67
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,700
and the secret of the copper coins.

68
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:47,830
Whether it's a blessing or a curse,

69
00:04:47,830 --> 00:04:49,430
he will choose for himself.'

70
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:50,360
Mo.

71
00:04:50,700 --> 00:04:52,000
Seeing this letter is like seeing me.

72
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,400
My journey is dangerous.

73
00:04:53,530 --> 00:04:54,530
If I can't return,

74
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,659
you should look for clues of the three coins

75
00:04:56,659 --> 00:04:58,530
and go straight to the Tianji Pavilion.

76
00:04:58,530 --> 00:05:00,360
On the ninth floor of the Black Tower in the Directorate of Astronomy,

77
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:02,020
lies the answer I left for you.

78
00:05:02,030 --> 00:05:02,560
Way.

79
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,430
The sons of the Shen family

80
00:05:03,430 --> 00:05:03,930
Justice.

81
00:05:03,930 --> 00:05:05,760
must live for truth and justice.

82
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,130
Last words of Qingshan.

83
00:05:08,630 --> 00:05:09,960
Even if what you say is true,

84
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:11,160
why did you aid the wicked

85
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,560
and hunt down the investigators?

86
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,500
Because their eyes

87
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:14,430
are everywhere.

88
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,420
If I didn't put on this act,

89
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,400
how could I gain their trust?

90
00:05:18,730 --> 00:05:20,460
How could I survive until today

91
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:22,060
to give you this letter?

92
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,960
When the three coins unite,

93
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,230
the Tianji Map will appear.

94
00:05:25,230 --> 00:05:26,400
We are still missing my father's

95
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,460
Shen copper coin.

96
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:29,330
The third Shen copper coin

97
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:31,460
is right here in the Imperial Clan Court.

98
00:05:31,460 --> 00:05:32,460
It is directly related to

99
00:05:32,460 --> 00:05:34,190
your father's disappearance.

100
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:34,860
Think about it.

101
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:37,130
What does the last place your father appeared

102
00:05:37,130 --> 00:05:39,330
have to do with the Imperial Clan Court?

103
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,620
The case files.

104
00:05:41,060 --> 00:05:42,130
Before his disappearance,

105
00:05:42,130 --> 00:05:42,860
the last thing my father requested

106
00:05:42,860 --> 00:05:44,000
was the Imperial Clan Court's sealed file

107
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,930
on the former Directorate of Astronomy's

108
00:05:44,930 --> 00:05:46,390
Director's sudden death.

109
00:05:52,860 --> 00:05:54,860
By the oral decree of His Highness the Crown Prince,

110
00:05:54,860 --> 00:05:56,500
seal the Imperial Clan Court!

111
00:05:56,500 --> 00:05:58,000
Arrest the trespasser

112
00:05:58,030 --> 00:05:59,860
and thief of secrets, Shen Mo!

113
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:01,600
The Crown Prince's men are here.

114
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,630
I cannot be exposed.

115
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:05,290
Go quickly, I'll see you at the Tianji Pavilion.

116
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:07,360
Registrar Shen.

117
00:06:07,730 --> 00:06:10,060
His Highness the Crown Prince requests your presence.

118
00:06:10,060 --> 00:06:10,860
After you.
